org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.process.traversal.step

Interface ByModulating

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AggregateStep, DedupGlobalStep, GroupCountSideEffectStep, GroupCountStep, GroupSideEffectStep, GroupStep, MathStep, OrderGlobalStep, OrderLocalStep, PageRankVertexProgramStep, PathFilterStep, PathStep, PeerPressureVertexProgramStep, ProjectStep, SackValueStep, SampleGlobalStep, SelectOneStep, SelectStep, StoreStep, TreeSideEffectStep, TreeStep, WherePredicateStep

    public interface ByModulating
    A ByModulating step is able to take GraphTraversal.by() calls. All the methods have default implementations excecpt modulateBy(Traversal.Admin). In short, given a traversal, what should the ByModulating step do with it.
    Author:
    Marko A. Rodriguez (http://markorodriguez.com)
